## `@app/contracts` — Always Define First

Before touching either service, define the contract in `libs/contracts/src/`:

```typescript
// libs/contracts/src/auth/auth.patterns.ts
export const AUTH_PATTERNS = {
  NEW_ACTION: 'auth.newAction',
} as const;

// libs/contracts/src/auth/auth.payloads.ts
export interface NewActionPayload {
  readonly field: string;
}
```

Multi-file edit order:
1. `prisma/schema.prisma` (if DB change)
2. `libs/contracts/src/` — patterns + payload interfaces
3. `apps/auth-service/src/<feature>/dto/` — DTOs
4. `apps/auth-service/src/<feature>/<feature>.repository.ts`
5. `apps/auth-service/src/<feature>/<feature>.service.ts`
6. `apps/auth-service/src/<feature>/<feature>.controller.ts` (`@MessagePattern`)
7. `apps/api-gateway/src/<feature>/<feature>.controller.ts` (`ClientProxy.send`)
8. Tests

