## Quick Commands

```bash
# Development — start auth-service first, then gateway
pnpm start:auth          # TCP microservice on port 9012
pnpm start:gateway       # HTTP server on port 9011

# Build
pnpm build:auth
pnpm build:gateway

# Testing
pnpm test                # All unit tests
pnpm test:e2e            # E2E tests
pnpm test:cov            # Coverage

# Database
pnpm prisma migrate dev  # Create and apply migration
pnpm prisma generate     # Regenerate Prisma client
pnpm prisma studio       # Database GUI

# Code quality
pnpm lint
pnpm format
```

