### How to apply skill rules
1. Identify the task category (architecture → `arch-*`, auth → `security-*`, etc.)
2. Open the matching rule file — read the _incorrect_ example first
3. Generate code matching the _correct_ example, adapting to project-specific patterns
4. CRITICAL rules must never be violated; HIGH rules require justification if deviated from

